## What Unitrader Is

**Company:** Unitrading (UK-based, global market)
**Product:** Unitrader — AI-powered trading SaaS platform
**Target market:** 650M+ global traders
**Business model:** $9.99/month subscription, 14-day free trial, users keep 100% of profits
**Vision:** Unicorn-scale — 28 AI agents in a unified symbiotic learning system

**Core concept:** Users sign up, name their own AI trader companion (e.g. "TradeMaster",
"CryptoKing"), connect their exchange account, and the AI trades crypto/stocks/forex
automatically on their behalf. Users keep all profits. Unitrader charges only the subscription.

