## Tech Stack

### Backend
- **Framework:** FastAPI (async)
- **ORM:** async SQLAlchemy
- **Database:** Supabase PostgreSQL 17.6
  - Session Pooler, port 5432
  - NullPool (required for PgBouncer transaction mode)
  - Never use regular pool — causes prepared statement conflicts
- **Auth:** Clerk (never build custom auth — always use Clerk)
- **Payments:** Stripe
- **Monitoring:** Sentry
- **Email:** Resend (NOT SendGrid — this decision is final)
- **Deployment:** Railway (auto-deploys from GitHub)

### Frontend
- **Framework:** Next.js 14
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS
- **Auth:** Clerk (`@clerk/nextjs`)
- **API client:** Axios (typed, in `lib/api.ts`)
- **Deployment:** Vercel (root directory: `unitrader-bot/frontend`)

### AI
- **Provider:** Anthropic Claude API
- **Model:** claude-sonnet (latest)
- **Usage:** 3 agents currently — trading, conversation, content/social

### Exchanges (Paper Trading in dev, Live in prod)
- **Stocks/ETFs:** Alpaca
  - Paper: `https://paper-api.alpaca.markets`
  - Live: `https://api.alpaca.markets`
- **Crypto:** Binance (primary), Coinbase Advanced Trade (adding)
  - Paper: `https://testnet.binance.vision`
  - Live: `https://api.binance.com`
- **Forex:** OANDA
  - Paper: `https://api-fxpractice.oanda.com`
  - Live: `https://api-fxtrade.oanda.com`

