## Background Loops (in main.py)

```
# Trading loop — runs every 5 minutes
# Fetches market data -> runs trading_agent -> executes trades for active users

# Monitor loop — runs every 1 minute
# Checks open positions -> enforces stop-loss/take-profit -> circuit breakers

# Content scheduler — hourly
# Daily: social posts | Weekly: blog posts | Monthly: performance reports

# Email scheduler — daily 9am UTC
# Trial drip emails at day 7, 3, 1, 0

# Learning hub — hourly
# Cross-agent pattern discovery and instruction updates
```

