## When Adding New Features — Checklist

- [ ] Does it need a DB model change? -> update `models.py` + migration
- [ ] Does it need new env vars? -> add to `config.py` + `.env.example` + Railway
- [ ] Does it need auth? -> use `get_current_user` dependency
- [ ] Does it handle user funds/keys? -> use Fernet encryption
- [ ] Does it call an exchange? -> check `TRADING_MODE` first
- [ ] Does it need tests? -> yes, always
- [ ] Does it need a frontend component? -> follow existing Tailwind dark theme
- [ ] Does it affect billing/trial? -> test Stripe webhook flow

